NAME
    MAN - Display manual pages

SYNOPSIS
    MAN <command>

DESCRIPTION
    Displays the manual page for the specified command.
    The manual pages are stored as text files in the /MAN/
    directory with a .man extension.

    The output is paginated. Press any key to advance to the
    next page, or 'q' to quit.

EXAMPLES
    MAN DIR
    MAN COPY
    MAN MAN

SEE ALSO
    HELP
